314
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,080
It must be a success.

315
00:24:24,480 --> 00:24:25,910
Please take me back.

316
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:28,720
Try again.

317
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,080
We will succeed.

318
00:24:32,190 --> 00:24:33,030
Let's do it again.

319
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,240
Why are you praying to a dagger

320
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,520
early in the morning?

321
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:40,360
What are you doing?

322
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:44,600
I am praying.

323
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:46,550
I hope for world peace.

324
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,360
What time is it now?

325
00:24:50,360 --> 00:24:51,880
Aren't we supposed to hurry back?

326
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,840
Get up quickly.

327
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:53,680
Let's go.

328
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:54,840
Hurry up.

329
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:09,670
Let me see.

330
00:25:12,430 --> 00:25:13,270
It's okay.

331
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,080
How to get up there?

332
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,320
Follow me.

333
00:25:36,030 --> 00:25:37,290
(Since I've been here,
just settle down.)

334
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:39,110
(It seems)

335
00:25:39,670 --> 00:25:41,000
(I can only wait for it to happen.)

336
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,430
(She cares so much about the Liuguang.)

337
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:48,640
(There is a totem of the Isolated Island
on the Liuguang.)

338
00:25:50,190 --> 00:25:52,270
(And she is immune to all poisons.)

339
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,560
(It seems she is undoubtedly
from the Isolated Island.)

340
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:00,190
(She keeps saying she wants to go home.)

341
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:02,440
(Does she mean)

342
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:04,640
