343
00:26:06,430 --> 00:26:07,270
Your Highness.

344
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,600
Why are you looking at me?

345
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,910
It seems you really like this dagger.

346
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,320
It's called Liuguang.

347
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:24,760
If you truly like it,

348
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:27,600
I can gift this dagger to you.

349
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:30,800
Really?

350
00:26:32,550 --> 00:26:33,390
Yes.

351
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:38,640
But isn't it a memento left
by your mother?

352
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,790
You saved my life,

353
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,720
so just consider it a gift of gratitude.

354
00:26:44,050 --> 00:26:44,890
Here.

355
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,670
Look, this dagger is very suitable
for a woman.

356
00:26:52,910 --> 00:26:54,880
Since it was left by my mother,

357
