to her daughter-in-law.

358
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:58,800
(Great.)

359
00:26:59,310 --> 00:27:00,670
(Now I can study it thoroughly.)

360
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:02,840
Alright.

361
