364
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:09,680
Go ahead.

365
00:27:10,910 --> 00:27:13,390
From now on,
you must not hide anything from me.

366
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:16,900
When have I ever hidden anything
from you?

367
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:21,910
At the Judicial Office, you managed
to escape on your own.

368
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:24,790
It is not something
an ordinary woman could do.

369
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:27,790
And in your competition with Chu Feiyan,

370
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,430
you surprised me a lot.

371
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:32,520
Besides, you saved me

372
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,430
and helped me guard the bordering land.

373
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:38,760
So from now on,

374
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:40,600
you must not hide anything from me.

375
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,390
We need

376
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:44,440
trust.

377
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:46,800
Alright.

378
00:27:47,150 --> 00:27:48,230
Rest assured, Your Highness.

379
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:50,550
I will pay my allegiance to you
from now on.

380
00:27:58,070 --> 00:27:58,910
Allegiance?

381
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,070
Do you want to be my soldier?

382
00:28:05,030 --> 00:28:05,870
Yes.

383
00:28:06,150 --> 00:28:07,520
