384
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:08,480
I will do my best.

385
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:20,600
Your Highness,

386
00:28:21,390 --> 00:28:24,240
actually, there's something
I'm curious about.

387
00:28:26,550 --> 00:28:27,790
It's about your mother.

388
00:28:28,550 --> 00:28:29,670
What kind of person was she?

389
00:28:33,390 --> 00:28:34,720
Before I can remember,

390
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:38,760
she was already gone.

391
00:28:42,430 --> 00:28:44,190
Then your days in the palace before

392
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:46,100
must have been quite difficult.

393
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,790
Any slight mistake

394
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:51,720
may cost me my life.

395
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:57,670
Since I was 14 years old,

396
00:28:57,670 --> 00:28:58,990
I have been asking Father for permission

397
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:00,910
to lead troops into battle.

398
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:04,790
At that time, it was not
for fame or status,

399
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:07,680
but to survive.

400
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:11,760
I also wanted a peaceful
and stable life,

401
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,880
but our Tianque's national strength
is not strong.

402
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:17,720
Besides Nanzhao and Tieyan,

403
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:20,720
the greatest threat to Tianque

404
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,840
comes from Dongling and Xiling.

405
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:24,760
Xiling has always occupied
Tianque's territory,

406
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:25,600
and Dongling

407
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:28,270
has never given up on its ambition
to revive for many years.

408
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,000
It's coveting the bordering land.

409
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:33,550
The only thing I want to do

410
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,430
is to protect Tianque's territory,

411
00:29:37,760 --> 00:29:38,910
so that the people of Tianque

412
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:41,390
do not become displaced.

413
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:19,600
Commander,

414
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:20,710
how is it? Any news?

415
00:30:20,710 --> 00:30:22,000
The soldiers of the Thirteen Riders

416
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,120
went out in four or five groups,

417
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:24,200
but none have found His Highness

418
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,300
or the Fourth Princess Consort.

419
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:27,960
Could it be that His Highness has...

420
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,800
Watch your mouth!

421
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:32,640
His Highness will be fine.

422
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,320
Pass my order.

423
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:36,800
Continue searching for them.

424
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:38,560
If they can't find His Highness,

425
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:40,720
- do not return to camp.
- Yes.

426
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:42,330
How did the war suddenly break out?

427
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,760
Yesterday,
the armored soldiers attacked.

428
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:45,670
The Fourth Prince is likely
in grave danger.

429
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:46,790
What should we do?

430
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:48,430
The King has arrived.

431
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:50,840
Your Majesty.

432
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:55,360
Father.

433
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:57,190
General Dugu Xianyun of Tieyan

434
00:30:57,190 --> 00:30:59,120
suddenly led an army of 100,00
to press the western border.

435
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,070
General Ouyang,
who guards the Western Pass,

436
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,960
only has 50,000 troops.
It's truly dangerous.

437
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:04,050
Father, Please issue an order

438
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:05,820
to mobilize Beiyue's White Tiger Army

439
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,790
to assist General Ouyang.

440
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,560
Second Prince,

441
00:31:10,190 --> 00:31:11,240
the battle has not yet begun.

442
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,670
Why assume defeat already?

443
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:14,760
With 50,000 against 100,000 troops,

444
00:31:15,670 --> 00:31:16,910
what are the chances of victory?

445
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,790
Now it's not clear
if the Fourth Prince still survives.

446
00:31:19,790 --> 00:31:22,360
But you're trying
to take his military power first.

447
00:31:22,360 --> 00:31:23,790
What's your respect to His Majesty?

448
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:28,580
It's not clear if Beiyue still survives.

449
00:31:29,430 --> 00:31:31,430
Tianque is also
at the brink of survival.

450
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,790
Are we to disregard the safety
of Tianque's people?

451
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,990
Do we really have to fight
with a ratio of five to ten?

452
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:39,360
It's true that Tieyan
is invading our western border.

453
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,600
But it will still take some time.

454
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:41,670
