with ill intentions.

457
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:48,560
Do you think

458
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,360
my fourth brother
can still come back alive?

459
00:31:53,430 --> 00:31:54,390
What should we do now?

460
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:55,310
Yes.

461
00:31:55,310 --> 00:31:56,360
What should we do?

462
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:58,150
