won't return?

463
00:31:58,840 --> 00:31:59,680
Father,

464
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:01,790
you saw it yourself on the day.

465
00:32:02,390 --> 00:32:03,240
Those armored men

466
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,190
were targeting Beiyue.

467
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:16,070
Have you found out yet?

468
00:32:17,150 --> 00:32:20,360
Who exactly sent those armored men?

469
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,720
Just as the armored men
launched their sneak attack,

470
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,670
Tieyan invaded.

471
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:25,760
It must be Tieyan who sent them.

472
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:30,790
We Tianque have always

473
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:34,120
adhered to the principle
of not attacking unless being attacked.

474
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:37,480
We have never had any conflicts
with Tieyan.

475
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:40,310
They dare to launch
such an unprovoked attack this time.

476
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,760
It is truly outrageous.

477
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:42,720
Yes.

478
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,550
So we must fight back

479
00:32:44,550 --> 00:32:45,720
and leave them with no survivors.

480
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,880
