481
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,720
are you determined
to take Beiyue's military power

482
00:32:57,190 --> 00:32:59,030
for your uncle?

483
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,190
Father, you misunderstand me.

484
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,670
It's not that I want
Beiyue's military power.

485
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:11,070
Only the White Tiger Army in the north
is closest to the west border now.

486
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:13,600
There is no other way.

487
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:15,160
Your Majesty,

488
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,840
if we mobilize the troops
from the northern border,

489
00:33:16,840 --> 00:33:18,100
the northern border will be in danger.

490
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:20,910
Prince Xiang and Princess Feiyan
of Xiling

491
00:33:20,910 --> 00:33:22,120
are still in the envoy courtyard.

492
00:33:24,150 --> 00:33:26,190
If they hear about this,

493
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:28,070
can you bear the responsibility?

494
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:35,270
Father,

495
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,860
I am willing to lead the troop
to guard the western border

496
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:39,000
and protect Tianque's territory.

497
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:42,120
This is a great opportunity.

498
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,360
Your Majesty,

499
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:47,990
if the Second Prince leads the troops,

500
00:33:48,390 --> 00:33:49,840
to assist General Ouyang,

501
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:52,000
we can definitely defeat Tieyan.

502
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:52,880
Your Majesty,

503
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:55,430
it must not be delayed.

504
00:33:55,430 --> 00:33:57,430
I hope you can make a decision now.

505
00:33:58,360 --> 00:34:01,910
Please make a decision, Your Majesty.

506
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:05,310
Father, please issue the decree

507
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:06,600
to hand the Tiger Tally over to me.

508
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,190
I guarantee

509
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:10,520
to retreat the Tieyan troops
within a month.

510
00:34:12,670 --> 00:34:14,190
Report.

511
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,390
Urgent report from the western border.

512
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:20,560
General Dugu Xianyun of Tieyan

513
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:22,150
is leading 3,000 elite soldiers
in the vanguard.

514
00:34:22,430 --> 00:34:24,110
They are only 50 miles
from the western border.

515
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,510
What...

516
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:29,040
What should we do now?

517
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:30,520
Father, please issue the decree

518
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:32,650
to order the White Tiger Army
to support the western border

519
00:34:32,720 --> 00:34:35,000
and reinforce General Ouyang's army.

520
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:37,040
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

521
00:34:37,040 --> 00:34:38,860
- Please reinforce the army.
- Please reinforce the army.

522
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:39,730
Please reinforce the army.

523
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:45,750
Someone.

524
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:47,520
Draft the decree

525
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:50,960
to appoint the Second Prince
as General of the West

526
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:54,080
who can mobilize 10,000 troops
from the outskirts of Tianque

527
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:55,720
to aid the western border,

528
00:34:55,720 --> 00:35:01,390
and to deploy the White Tiger Army
from the north to support the northwest.

529
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:02,230
Father.

530
00:35:02,520 --> 00:35:04,040
To take command of the White Tiger Army,

531
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:07,150
I need Sima Xun, the leader
of the Thirteen Riders

532
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:08,110
to join me.

533
00:35:11,540 --> 00:35:12,390
Approved.

534
00:35:12,390 --> 00:35:14,480
You are wise, Your Majesty.

535
00:35:18,910 --> 00:35:19,750
Make way quickly.

536
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:21,520
- Make way.
- Make way.

537
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:29,110
Did you dispatch the armored men?

538
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,390
What if I did?

539
00:35:34,910 --> 00:35:36,870
You knew I came for a marriage alliance.

540
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:39,000
Yet you wanted to kill Jun Beiyue.

541
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:42,320
You should be grateful now

542
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:43,480
that you lost to Han Ziqing.

543
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:45,670
Otherwise

544
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:48,040
you would be a widow now.

545
00:35:48,910 --> 00:35:50,150
Jun Beiyue cannot die.

546
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,600
Sis,

547
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:57,720
I don't care how infatuated you are.

548
00:35:57,720 --> 00:36:00,280
If you ruin Father's grand plan
of attacking Dongling,

549
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,720
no one will be able to save you.

550
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:05,910
Jun Beiyue

551
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,390
is the stumbling block on our way

552
00:36:08,390 --> 00:36:09,670
to attack Dongling.

553
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,870
Sooner or later, he must be removed.

554
00:36:13,870 --> 00:36:15,350
A marriage alliance is the best way.

555
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:17,150
It won't harm Jun Beiyue,

556
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:18,150
and we can use Tianque.

557
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,190
The plan is good,

558
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,630
but you were not skilled enough

559
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,080
and lost to a concubine's daughter.

560
00:36:27,830 --> 00:36:28,670
What can I do?

561
00:36:32,870 --> 00:36:34,190
Do you think I don't know?

562
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,350
Even without Dongling,

563
00:36:35,350 --> 00:36:37,040
you still wouldn't tolerate Jun Beiyue.

564
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,080
Because you are jealous of him,

565
00:36:38,870 --> 00:36:40,040
and that he is better than you.

566
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:49,960
Now, Jun Beiyue's dead body

567
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:52,040
is probably already cold.

568
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:55,240
How is he better than me?

569
00:36:57,720 --> 00:37:00,000
Clearly, you and Jun Beichen
are colluding,

570
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,110
and trying to get rid of Jun Beiyue.

571
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:04,240
If I tell the King of Tianque
about this...

572
00:37:08,690 --> 00:37:09,550
Try it.

573
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:11,080
I guarantee you will never see the sun

574
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,560
on the grasslands again.

575
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:13,590
You're too despicable.

576
00:37:14,570 --> 00:37:16,080
If Xiling falls into your hands
in the future,

577
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,280
it won't end well.

578
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:21,910
Chu Feiyan,

579
00:37:21,910 --> 00:37:23,320
relying on Father's favor,

580
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:24,670
can you be so disrespectful now?

581
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:28,520
Yes, I did collude with Jun Beichen,

582
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:30,760
but he also secretly colluded
with Tieyan

583
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:32,670
and attempted
to take Jun Beiyue's military power.

584
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:36,000
If others can use the scheme, so can I.

585
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:39,320
What's despicable about that?

586
00:37:46,630 --> 00:37:47,560
I will tell Father.

587
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,280
Father only wants one result.

588
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:56,920
It is

589
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:58,670
to control Tianque

590
00:37:59,830 --> 00:38:01,040
and conquer Dongling.

591
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,600
Sis,

592
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,560
pack up your things.

593
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,640
We should leave.

594
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,670
Shadow and the others

595
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:24,320
should be able to see the smoke
I just released.

596
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,150
I believe they will arrive soon.

597
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,430
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

598
00:38:48,520 --> 00:38:49,360
Something has happened.

599
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:52,430
- Where is the injury?
- Jun Beichen took the Tiger Tally

600
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:55,040
- to take over the main camp.
- It's nothing, just a minor injury.

601
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:58,630
Well, Shadow.

602
00:38:58,630 --> 00:38:59,470
Here.

603
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:01,240
Escort the Princess Consort back
to the mansion.

604
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:02,320
- Yes.
- Remember,

605
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,800
rest well after returning
to the mansion.

606
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:04,940
- Okay.
- Remember.

607
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:06,000
Do not wander around.

608
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:22,910
Report.

609
00:39:22,910 --> 00:39:24,280
- Commander.
- Speak up. What's the matter?

610
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:26,250
The Second Prince received
an imperial edict from the King

611
00:39:26,250 --> 00:39:27,830
to take over our main camp.

612
00:39:27,830 --> 00:39:28,670
What?

613
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,390
Second Prince,

614
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:37,350
what brings you here?

615
00:39:38,390 --> 00:39:39,430
Commander Sima.

616
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:41,520
The King has issued a decree

617
00:39:41,520 --> 00:39:43,800
to order you to join me
to the northern border

618
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,520
and assist me in mobilizing
the White Tiger Army.

619
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:47,280
White Tiger Army?

620
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:50,400
Second Prince.

621
00:39:50,870 --> 00:39:52,590
I must remind you

622
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:55,480
that you have no authority
to command the White Tiger Army.

623
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,080
Commander Sima,

624
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:01,390
this is the King's decree.

625
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:03,910
Are you going to defy the decree?

626
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,590
The Tieyan army is pressing
at the border.

627
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:08,720
The military situation is urgent.

628
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:11,630
I recommended you to the King.

629
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:14,110
After the Tieyan army retreats,

630
00:40:14,630 --> 00:40:16,520
the entire northern border
will be handed over to you.

631
00:40:17,350 --> 00:40:19,280
But your attitude

632
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:23,560
is making me troubled.

633
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:27,520
I am a soldier.

634
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,590
Without the King's Tiger Tally,

635
00:40:31,390 --> 00:40:32,430
I will obey no one.

636
00:40:33,910 --> 00:40:34,750
Second Prince,

637
00:40:35,870 --> 00:40:37,320
you should give up on this idea.

638
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,080
Someone.

639
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:46,240
Hand over the Tiger Tally,

640
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:48,760
and I will spare your life.

641
00:40:49,350 --> 00:40:50,430
Don't even think about it.

642
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:54,640
Jun Beichen,

643
00:40:55,870 --> 00:40:58,280
you will never be able
to compare with the Fourth Prince.

644
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:03,320
The Fourth Prince has always acted
with integrity,

645
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:04,360
and you

646
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:09,040
are nothing but a schemer
who plots behind the scenes.

647
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:11,960
The Fourth Prince

648
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,960
will never spare you.

649
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:16,870
I will fulfill your wish then.

650
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:25,600
Your Highness.

651
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,120
Beiyue,

652
00:41:37,080 --> 00:41:38,320
why have you returned?

653
00:41:40,150 --> 00:41:42,350
You didn't expect me to return alive,
did you?

654
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,190
I, I...

655
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:46,110
That's not what I mean.

656
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:51,000
You hurt my people while I was away.

657
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:54,190
What is the meaning of this?

658
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:58,870
Beiyue, you misunderstood.

659
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:00,910
This is Father's decree.

660
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:03,590
You dare to touch my people.

661
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:05,720
Take him away!

662
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:07,470
Wait!

663
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,240
Who dares to touch me?

664
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:12,870
It's between us brothers.

665
00:42:12,870 --> 00:42:14,190
We can discuss it in front of Father.

666
00:42:14,830 --> 00:42:16,280
If you want to use lynching,

667
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:20,560
ask the Tiger Tally in my hand first.

668
00:42:22,190 --> 00:42:23,030
Your Highness.

669
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,040
You want to see Father, right?

670
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:34,000
I will tell Father about

671
00:42:34,560 --> 00:42:36,520
what you have done one by one clearly.

672
00:43:40,270 --> 00:43:41,110
Attention!

673
00:43:54,320 --> 00:43:55,160
Your Highness, be careful.

674
00:43:55,630 --> 00:43:56,470
Release the arrows.

675
00:44:11,130 --> 00:44:12,310
Quickly go and get reinforcements!

676
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:13,160
Yes.

677
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:14,640
Go.

678
00:44:47,090 --> 00:44:51,160
♪Memories drift afar♪

679
00:44:53,510 --> 00:44:59,350
♪Gather into love, opening our hearts♪

680
00:44:59,710 --> 00:45:02,690
♪Like the sweet scent of flowers♪

681
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:06,000
♪It heals old scars♪

682
00:45:06,350 --> 00:45:10,780
♪May we brave through life's trials together♪

683
00:45:13,180 --> 00:45:17,460
♪Time flows peacefully like a stream♪

684
00:45:19,880 --> 00:45:25,560
♪Into the sea it merges, where desolation goes♪

685
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:32,190
♪Washed by time's endless cycle♪

686
00:45:32,560 --> 00:45:38,030
♪Old sorrows fade away♪

687
00:45:39,520 --> 00:45:45,390
♪May time reach through longing♪

688
00:45:45,760 --> 00:45:51,140
♪To where you are♪

689
00:45:51,930 --> 00:45:58,570
♪No matter how long, I'll never forget♪

690
00:45:59,240 --> 00:46:04,320
♪Crossing the night sky,
with the moon so bright♪

691
00:46:05,880 --> 00:46:11,710
♪May light cut through the darkness
of the night♪

692
00:46:12,060 --> 00:46:18,010
♪To where I found you♪

693
00:46:18,210 --> 00:46:21,550
♪No matter the distance♪

694
00:46:21,880 --> 00:46:25,310
♪I'll fly to your side♪

695
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:31,450
♪Through time and beyond♪

696
00:46:35,470 --> 00:46:41,680
♪May light cut through the darkness
of the night♪

697
00:46:41,680 --> 00:46:47,620
♪To where I found you♪

698
00:46:47,810 --> 00:46:51,080
♪No matter the distance♪

699
00:46:51,520 --> 00:46:54,850
♪I'll fly to your side♪

700
00:46:55,200 --> 00:47:00,810
♪Through time and beyond♪

701
00:47:08,360 --> 00:47:10,340
♪Through time♪

702
